---
title: Crispy Shallot, Prawn & Chilli Oil Tofu with Corn Rice & Asian Greens
description: Meet your new weeknight superstar! Velvety tofu & prawns takes centre stage, draped in a spicy-sweet chilli crisp shallot oil that’s as bold as it is addictive. Fluffy rice speckled with sweet bursts of corn adds a cosy, golden touch, while vibrant greens bring a fresh, crisp contrast. Perfect for those nights when you crave something simple, satisfying and packed with flavour!

